05cfc3e219","tid":187651,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UeU96c1ic1aRLDYKMv7EJgIUeHgojy8p1V9oEzney8skxv848z2cibFLjRoNzHzfMjsc5b4WAcwic9vtawHibfn7sQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fread.html5.qq.com%2Fimage%3Fsrc%3Dforum%26q%3D5%26r%3D0%26imgflag%3D7%26imageUrl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUeU96c1ic1aRLDYKMv7EJgIUeHgojy8p1V9oEzney8skxv848z2cibFLjRoNzHzfMjsc5b4WAcwic9vtawHibfn7sQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg&h=4cdeebab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf80316d7976da18f4e63e0d1b749a850ae3922d","tid":187651,"uid":3004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"蝗化<br />\n大媽都無人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿嬸就阿嬸啦大媽"},{"pid":"f55b42d37a425514ab0f83a41788dbed119f4065","tid":187651,"uid":1345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"係咪得返裕華個啲先有得賣？"},{"pid":"266d9f3b185cb37a54141e12582bf5a43f0a76ff","tid":187651,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪得返裕華個啲先有得賣？</blockquote><br />\n周街都有喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  差在有冇紅色盒果隻姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 紅色盒果隻係無蔗糖版，但我覺得無原味咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141adbfe575dc6b74e2a5a6907f341de13e3b2d4","tid":187651,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/645000/649451/20150702081166416641_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F645000%2F649451%2F20150702081166416641_1024.jpg&h=e073819c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個嗰陣見到呢張笑到癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />卡卡人生污點</blockquote><br />\n早幾年係巴士車身仲見到呢個廣告，依家仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年卡卡比佢盜用左呢張相拍廣告，佢本人凈係食左餐飯咋，當年仲告鳩個賤女人，話佢侵犯肖像權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e6bf774060c7dd712981a62a5b1f3af7c67bcc","tid":187651,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"佢換左包裝之後覺得食落口個下唔同左味<br />\n以前真係成日當糖咁食"},{"pid":"5911498125bbef5057b2261121456c3cbe2c3693","tid":187651,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>包裝盒原本的老先生是金嗓子喉寶的發明人&mdash;&mdash;華東師範大學王耀發教授，而真正的當家人，是金嗓子控股集團有限公司董事長江佩珍。<br />\n<br />\n　　金嗓子集團所獲的此專利配方是王耀發教授無償捐獻的。當年江佩珍團隊的執著真誠，感動了王教授，洽談進展順利。 &ldquo;合作成功，我們決定將發明人王教授的頭像印在產品包裝盒上，讓知識產權得到全社會的認同，在當時，這種舉措為數不多。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n        而如今，金嗓子喉寶的市場地位已經不可替代，為了鞏固市場地位和形象，避免潛在利益糾紛的風險，2015年所有的包裝都更換成了江佩珍女士頭像，並製作了大量以江佩珍為主體的宣傳（廣告）物料。繼續使用原始的手法大量進行平面推廣。</blockquote><br />\n即係起咗朵就一腳兜開個原創者啦，典型支那人處事手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n畀小小甜頭氹你落搭，然後一腳伸開你。<br />\n大陸對香港亦然，然而香港太多自私自利嘅港豬。<br />\n<br />\n港豬會醒？太陽都由閪邊升起！"},{"pid":"0f2f1e19aef8f8de1f2d9519baadabe4159d3aba","tid":187651,"uid":76608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0u57Hg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0u57Hg0.jpg&h=e4cad834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n人樣黎???</blockquote><br />\n你識咩<br />\n人地上市嗰陣幾撚霸氣<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20150715/photo/bkn-20150715101040111-0715_00842_001_01b.jpg?20150715133618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20150715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20150715101040111-0715_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20150715133618&h=9c25d22e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，成個食神入面薛家燕咁，做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個肚就黎跌出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑到停唔撚到，咩樣咩姿勢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講都唔知轉咗樣，唔係成日食<br />\n不過金嗓子真係好有效"},{"pid":"b20a4631cf29eef9d95eb8cc487a3be5dda4eb2c","tid":187651,"uid":76608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問好耐 以前阿伯慈祥好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前仲可以幫啊伯加返d 頭髮上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無咁玩過啊 <br />\n<br />\n以前啲盒掉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想keep返都無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好後悔<br />\n擁有既時候無珍惜<br />\n到失去左先知道後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哩度有無巴打有舊盒俾個我<br />\nSo後悔now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱揾到枱頭有2個，可以俾1個你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntg: janxjan"},{"pid":"c0f0d0c31294f609b8db6c957c7fb93d6c4fc6d2","tid":187651,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rthk9.rthk.hk/APSuppics/mfile_55_1116123_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frthk9.rthk.hk%2FAPSuppics%2Fmfile_55_1116123_1.jpg&h=6713d21a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"739414e210edccd2a486a7d3d5ece0e3cb3e0eb9","tid":187651,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161019/large/1476882652_4f69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161019%2Flarge%2F1476882652_4f69.jpg&h=be3c9016&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}